Key decisions:

Click a set → activates it + opens the right drawer
Active row gets a left border accent + subtle background
Badge = instrument count, updates live when you add/remove
No inline expansion — the list never grows
+ NEW is at the top right of the panel header, not floating at the top of the page
DELETE moves to the right drawer (detail view), out of the list — reduces accidental deletes
Step 3 — Refactor the Center Panel
The center panel owns search + instrument grid. It gets the full remaining width.

Top controls bar:


Search by:  [Issuer ____________]  [Paste ISINs]
Rename ISINS button → Paste ISINs (or Bulk ISIN Search)
Remove the "Add instrument(s) to comp sets" dropdown from here entirely — it moves to the tray (Step 5)
The controls bar is position: sticky; top: 0 so it stays visible when the grid scrolls
The AgGrid:

Takes remaining height of the center panel
Row selection via checkbox column (leftmost) + shift-click range
When 0 rows selected → tray is hidden
When ≥1 row selected → tray appears (Step 5)
